export default function IlustracionConfirmacion(props) {

        justifyContent="unset"
        overflow="hidden"
        position="absolute"
        top="-2.86%"
        bottom="-2.81%"
        left="-3.87%"
        right="-3.89%"
        padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"
        {...getOverrideProps(overrides, "Capa_1")}

        <View
          padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"

          justifyContent="unset"

          left="1.28%"
          right="-1.28%"
          {...getOverrideProps(overrides, "Group")}
        >
          <Text
            fontFamily="Inter"

            whiteSpace="pre-wrap"
            children="Tu pago se ha realizado
de forma exitosa"
            {...getOverrideProps(
              overrides,
              "Tu pago se ha realizado de forma exitosa"
            )}
          ></Text>
          <Image
            width="100%"
            height="80.39%"
            display="block"
            gap="unset"
            alignItems="unset"
            justifyContent="unset"
            position="absolute"
            top="19.61%"
            bottom="0%"
            left="0%"
            right="0%"
            padding="0px 0px 0px 0px"
            objectFit="cover"
            src="/img/imgConfir.png"
            {...getOverrideProps(overrides, "3")}
